item.title: CVE-2020-2195|2024-08-04T07:01:41.072Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20compact%20columns%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Compact Columns Plugin 1.11 and earlier displays the unprocessed job description in tooltips, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting vulnerability that can be exploited by users with Job/Configure permission.
